# AI Model Testbed (bootstrap)

A minimal, clean structure to test different AI models behind one interface.

## Quick start

```bash
uv venv && uv pip install -e ".[dev]"
# or: python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate && pip install -e ".[dev]"
pytest -q
```

## Layout
- `config/models.yaml` — model registry (name, endpoint, key)
- `src/ai_testbed/config/loader.py` — typed config loader
- `src/ai_testbed/connectors/` — model connectors (start with `mock`)
- `src/ai_testbed/harness/test_harness.py` — tiny test harness
- `tests/` — unit tests and sample cases
